NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::NoSmartCommentsTests - Release tests for version
    numbers

VERSION
    version 0.001

SYNOPSIS
    In "dist.ini":

        [NoSmartCommentTests]

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following file:

      xt/release/no-smart-comments.t - test to ensure no Smart::Comments

AUTHOR
    Chris Weyl <cweyl@alumni.drew.edu>

